OL,3,CCrash involving helicopter shuts key
OL,4,Croads in Devon
OL,6,FEmergency services are at the scene of
OL,7,Fa crash involving a helicopter in a
OL,8,Ffield at Sourton Down, near
OL,9,FOkehampton, in Devon.
OL,11,FThe A386 is shut northbound from the
OL,12,FA30 at Sourton Cross to A3079
OL,13,FHolsworthy Road at Fowley Cross.
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police say they
OL,16,Fwill share more updates when they have
OL,17,Fthem.
