OL,3,CCrash involving helicopter shuts key
OL,4,Croads in Devon
OL,6,FIn a statement on Facebook, the force
OL,7,Fsaid: "Several road closures are in
OL,8,Fplace around the A386 and A30 Sourton
OL,9,FCross slip and services area. The
OL,10,Fincident is ongoing."
